<% content_for(:title, "About - Autobiography Template") %>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">About This Autobiography</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      A digital journey through life's most meaningful moments, memories, and milestones.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <!-- Profile Section -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-1">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-400 to-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <img src="/your-profile-photo.jpg" 
               alt="Your Profile Photo" 
               class="w-full h-full object-cover"
               onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';" />
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Welcome to [Your Name]'s Story</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          This digital autobiography template helps preserve life's precious moments for future generations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Story Section -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-2">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">[Your Name]'s Story</h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 space-y-4">
          <p>
            Welcome to this digital autobiography template—a customizable platform for collecting and sharing life's chapters. 
            This template serves as both a personal memoir foundation and a legacy tool for future generations.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Each chapter represents a significant period, experience, or milestone that can be customized with your own stories. From childhood 
            memories to professional achievements, from family moments to personal growth, this template helps you capture 
            the essence of your unique journey.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            The photo gallery complements written memories with visual snapshots of important moments, 
            places, and people. Together, they create a comprehensive portrait 
            of your life's story.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            This autobiography template is more than just a collection of pages—it's a customizable gift for your family, friends, 
            and future generations who want to understand their heritage and the experiences that shaped 
            their family history.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4 border-t border-gray-200 pt-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">What You'll Find Here</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Life chapters with rich storytelling</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start justify-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Photo gallery with memories</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start justify-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Personal reflections and insights</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start justify-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Family history and heritage</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <div class="text-center mt-12">
    <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Start Exploring</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        Dive into the sample chapters and discover how to customize this template with your own life moments.
      </p>
      <div class="space-x-4">
        <%= link_to "Read Chapters", list_chapters_path, 
            class: "bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-medium transition-colors" %>
        <%= link_to "View Gallery", photos_path, 
            class: "bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 text-gray-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-medium transition-colors" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
